WEBVTT

NOTE This video is silent. Captions describe the on-screen actions.

00:00.000 --> 00:04.000
The XposedOrNot home page opens, offering a free check for email
addresses exposed in data breaches.

00:04.000 --> 00:08.000
An email address is typed into the search box and Check Now is selected.

00:08.000 --> 00:12.000
Results appear instantly: the email was exposed in 3 breaches,
including 500px, MyFitnessPal and Pemiblanc.

00:12.000 --> 00:16.500
Detailed Report opens a full analysis with a yearly breach trend chart
and a risk score gauge reading 57, a medium risk.

00:16.500 --> 00:22.000
The impact assessment lists compromised passwords, personal information
exposure and phishing risks, each with a recommended action.

00:22.000 --> 00:26.000
A table summarises each breach and the number of exposed records,
followed by the exposed data grouped into categories.

00:26.000 --> 00:30.000
Charts break down password risks, top exposed breaches and
industry-wise exposure.

00:30.000 --> 00:34.000
A timeline visualises all exposed breaches, with options to enable
alerts for future breaches and share the tool.
